message.entry: When the ''Block'' method is specified, ''Upright'' is ignored.
Cannot use KAZEPoints in code generation.
To extract KAZE feature vectors, use ''FeatureSize'' instead of ''SURFSize''.
Both ''SURFSize'' and ''FeaturesSize'' cannot be specified. Use ''FeatureSize'' only.
Upright flag is not supported with ORB extraction method.
To extract ORB feature vectors, use ORBPoints only.
